{"tid":1796132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日實在不值得慶祝，約會的人請想想坐牢的人","createTime":"2019-12-24T11:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T11:44:56.000Z","uid":269202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2df10ea4740d3fc27a5f2bf425162ba4216bb3ec","tid":1796132,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"「酒醉的人哪，要清醒哭泣； 好酒的人哪，都要為甜酒哀號， 因為從你們的口中斷絕了。」<br />\n‭‭約珥書‬ ‭1:5‬ ‭CUNP-神‬‬<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bible.com/46/jol.1.5.cunp-神\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bible.com%2F46%2Fjol.1.5.cunp-%E7%A5%9E&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAYxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=7e861bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bible.com/46/jol.1.5.cunp-神</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節本是記念耶穌降生作救主，人死不再是終點<br />\n罪由神兒子承擔，何解在一眾被濫捕被打至傷殘的抗爭者面前，我們有臉面去慶祝商業節日？"}]}